\emph default
Useful if you need to re-record a section of music after editing has started.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Audition (A)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Description:
\emph default
 Mouse-driven auditioning of folders or individual tracks that uses intelligent
 mixer views.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Notes: 
\emph default
Simply hover the mouse over an area of the project and press A to begin
 auditioning the audio.
 Hover over a folder track to hear the complete mix or a single track within
