\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Whole Project View Horizontal (`)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Description: 
\emph default
Zoom to show the whole project horizontally.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Notes: 
\emph default
Very useful for a birdseye view of your project so you can navigate to another
 section.
 If there are multiple folders, the script collapses them.
 If fewer than two folders, the script respects the current folder view.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Whole Project View Vertical (Ctrl + `)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Description: 
\emph default
Zoom to show the whole project vertically.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Notes: 
\emph default
Very useful for a birdseye view of your project so you can see all vertical
